input: Go ̈ teborgsvarvet is an annual half marathon running event in Gothenburg , Sweden .
target: Go ̈ teborgsvarvet ( -RSB- ) is an annual half marathon running competition in Gothenburg , Sweden ( often called the Gothenburg Half Marathon in English ) .

input: In common law legal systems , a precedent or authority is a legal case that establishes a principle or rule .
target: In common law legal systems , precedent is a principle or rule established in a previous legal case that is either binding on or persuasive for a court or other tribunal when deciding subsequent cases with similar issues or facts .

input: The officers of arms earn money from their own private practices in heraldry and genealogy .
target: In addition to their official duties , the heralds have for many centuries undertaken private practice in heraldry and genealogy , for which professional fees are charged .
